### FeatureToggle Specification

```
Location: components/ui/FeatureToggle.tsx
Type: Functional component
Props:
  slug: string (feature identifier)
  scope: 'global' | 'campus' | 'grade' | 'class'
  enabled: boolean (current effective state)
  onToggle: (slug: string, scope: string, enabled: boolean) => void
  disabled?: boolean (true when teacher viewing non-class scope, or during mutation)
  source?: string (for inherited state display)
  className?: string

Layout:
  Horizontal row: label (left) + toggle switch (right)
  Toggle track: w-11 h-6 rounded-full, bg-muted (off) or bg-primary (on)
  Toggle knob: w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-white, translate-x on/off
  Transition: transition-colors duration-200

Behavior:
  - When disabled=true: opacity-50, pointer-events-none
  - When source is not the current scope: show InheritedIndicator below
  - On toggle: call onToggle with new boolean value
  - During mutation: show brief disabled state until mutation resolves
```

